	dprr:hasNoteText "An officer under the Triumvirs who issued coins at the naval base at Lipara in 37-36 (MRR 2.406). The nomen may be Calpenus or Calpetanus or Calpurnius. See Wiseman, NM 280, no. 527.\n" .
